Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.67,0:01:06.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:06.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.38,0:01:07.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:07.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming right up
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.96,0:01:08.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:08.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.38,0:01:09.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:09.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me a second
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.42,0:01:11.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜上菜上菜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:11.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up, up, up
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.92,0:01:15.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:15.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.59,0:01:19.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么还没去倒垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:19.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you taken out the trash?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.35,0:01:26.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都忙不过来了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:26.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm swamped, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.06,0:01:28.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛披着毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:28.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing a towel?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.65,0:01:32.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一眼都能看得出来我在蒸桑拿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:32.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, obviously, I was in me sauna
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.73,0:01:35.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当经理可辛苦了  知道不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:35.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Being a manager is hard work, you know?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.03,0:01:36.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你表现得再好点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:36.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have to do better
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不能帮我一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you help me a little bit?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.87,0:01:42.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经理才不做脏活累活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:42.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A manager does not do grunt work
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.37,0:01:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是章鱼哥这种员工的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what Squidwards are for
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.83,0:01:53.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我理应当上经理  整天无所事事才对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:53.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I deserve to be manager and sit on my butt all day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.00,0:01:55.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我有机会升职吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:55.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But will I ever get promoted?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.67,0:01:58.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你已经当废物当烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:58.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you tired of being a loser?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.43,0:02:01.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  谁在说话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:01.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, who said that?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.39,0:02:05.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不想当个废热狗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:05.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you rather be a weenie?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not exactly
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.35,0:02:11.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废热狗儿童乐园正在招募经理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:11.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Weenie Hut Jr's is now hiring managers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,240)}儿童乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(954,692)}经理
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.73,0:02:14.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的职务将包括
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:14.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your responsibilities will include
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.11,0:02:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放松享清福  让机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kicking back, relaxing, and letting robots
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把脏活累活都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,do all of the grunt work
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.45,0:02:23.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:23.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Righteous
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来儿童乐园找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Apply now to Weenie Hut Jr.'s
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.50,0:02:31.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成为我们这家企业机器的关键齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:31.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and become a pivotal cog in the corporate machine
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A manager?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's for me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.13,0:02:41.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:41.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.01,0:02:46.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个该死的收银员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:46.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is that blasted cashier?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.18,0:02:47.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经迟到一小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:47.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's already an hour late
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.10,0:02:50.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个老太婆谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:50.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And who the heck is this old lady?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我闻到了腌椰菜味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I smell pickles
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  你不觉得章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, isn't Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些天帅气得不得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,looking better than ever these days?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.11,0:02:57.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:57.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那又不是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ain't Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.24,0:03:02.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她怎么戴着章鱼哥的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:02.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is she wearing his hat?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他失踪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he lost?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他怎么会迟到这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is he so late?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.29,0:03:14.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:14.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming to find you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(718,374)}儿童乐园
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.05,0:03:23.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:23.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到你可真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I found you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.23,0:03:31.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来带你回到蟹堡王去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:31.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get you back to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.73,0:03:32.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:32.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think so
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.65,0:03:39.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不可能回到蟹堡王去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:39.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not going back to the Krusty Krab ever
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.45,0:03:45.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我现在是这企业机器的关键齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:45.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because now I am a pivotal cog in the corporate machine
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.95,0:03:46.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:46.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.66,0:03:47.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来感觉很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:47.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds horrible
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.87,0:03:48.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:48.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.79,0:03:52.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来我就是这里的经理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:52.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sounds like I'm the manager here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(328,736)}经理
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.58,0:03:57.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是说我可以来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:57.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which also means I decide
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.34,0:04:00.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁能留  谁不能留
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:04:00.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who stays and who goes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废热狗机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Weenie Bots
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把这个乌合之众踢出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kick out this riffraff
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.34,0:04:07.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得令  废热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:07.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As you command, Weenie
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  废热狗机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, Weenie Bots
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,身为你们新任的经理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As your new manager
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.44,0:04:19.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要在此做出一些改变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:19.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be making a few changes around here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.24,0:04:25.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点唱机里的所有音乐全都要换成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:25.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All music in the jukebox will now be
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轻柔爵士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,smooth jazz
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有废热狗主题作品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All Weenie-themed art
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.62,0:04:33.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都要换成艺术作品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:33.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will now be fine art
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.00,0:04:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后  无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, lastly, under no circumstances
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.17,0:04:44.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不准有谁打断我的经理时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:44.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is anyone allowed to interrupt my manager time
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.47,0:04:52.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当经理可辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:52.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Being a manager is hard work
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.23,0:04:56.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废热狗老板  你得出去倒垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:56.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boss Weenie, you must take out the trash
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你为什么不倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why can't you do it?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.52,0:05:02.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的扩展电源线够不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:02.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My extension cord won't reach
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是要好过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still better
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.87,0:05:08.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个蟹堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:08.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Than the Krusty
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.12,0:05:10.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:10.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open that door
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.26,0:05:27.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:27.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Celebration
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Celebration
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.61,0:05:46.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:46.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are back
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Weenie
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.55,0:06:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该来做点经理工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for a little managerial work
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.22,0:06:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如何修理无法无天的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"How to Repair Unruly Robots"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:10.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,518)}如何修理\N无法无天的机器人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.19,0:06:22.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样应该就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:22.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ought to do the trick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.90,0:06:28.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废热狗机器人  给我个热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:28.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Weenie Bots, bring me a weenie
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  经理先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Manager
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.58,0:06:40.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们变成完美员工了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:40.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're perfect employees now
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废热狗机器人  管店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Weenie Bots, run the store
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.67,0:06:48.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要独享经理时间去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:48.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm having manager time
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  经理先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:23.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1086,302)}双童周三
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经理先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Manager
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.38,0:07:31.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不出来我在睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:31.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see I'm trying to sleep?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.18,0:07:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说负责经理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean manage
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.43,0:07:36.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废热狗儿童乐园公司总裁要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The president
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the Weenie Hut Corporation is arriving
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.78,0:07:57.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好个废热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:57.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a weenie
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.33,0:08:01.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,热狗小狗热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:01.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Weenie J. Weiner
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小表示的是儿童
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The J stands for Junior
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.37,0:08:06.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定就是章鱼哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:06.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must be Squidward Q. Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哥表示的是大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Q stands for Quincy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.55,0:08:12.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:12.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To what do I owe this honor?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.09,0:08:16.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你大获成功  引起了总部的热议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:14.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your success has been all the buzz
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,down at headquarters
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.10,0:08:22.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我就过来给你升职
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:22.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I came straightaway to offer you the big promotion
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.85,0:08:26.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算有人能认可我的价值了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:26.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, someone recognizes my worth
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你得先参加一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, first, you'll need to take
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高级经理培训
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,our upper-management course
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.49,0:08:36.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请登上我的废热狗直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:36.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, step into my weeniecopter
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.79,0:08:52.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临废热狗成年乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:52.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Weenie Hut Senior's
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.18,0:09:00.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你  废热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:09:00.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Weenie
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.01,0:09:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你  废热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Weenie
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你  废热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Weenie
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.69,0:09:08.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边有好多机器人在工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:08.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There sure are a lot of robots working here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.36,0:09:11.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  机器人更加高效
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:11.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, robots are so much more efficient
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更加卫生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and sanitary
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临  废热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Weenie
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.82,0:09:21.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:21.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, have a seat
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.37,0:09:25.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躺平  脑袋只想着热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:25.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now lie back and think of weenies
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.75,0:09:29.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是个什么经理培训啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:29.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What exactly is this management course?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,告诉你吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.75,0:09:33.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要把你变成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:33.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we are going to turn you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.09,0:09:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能力范围中最为高效的经理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,into the most efficient manager you can be
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.01,0:09:42.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是要把你变成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:42.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By turning you into a
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Robot
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.60,0:09:46.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:46.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, a robot
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一听就很
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,well, that sounds just--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这就是在救你啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are helping you, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.49,0:09:55.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会成为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:55.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will be
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.57,0:09:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One of us
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy there, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here to save you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们怎么会知道我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you even know I was here?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you were in danger
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都起章鱼感应了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My squiddy sense was tingling
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.40,0:10:37.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想知道那什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:37.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to know what that means
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.44,0:10:39.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快救我出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:39.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just get me out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.16,0:10:42.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  装载炮弹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:42.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, SpongeBob, load her up
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.16,0:10:44.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:44.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's ready
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心你的头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch your head
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.33,0:10:52.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夹啊夹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:52.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pinchy, pinchy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.34,0:10:56.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可爱可爱可爱可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:56.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cutie, cutie, cutie, cutie
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.01,0:11:01.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个婴儿宝宝要炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:01.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That brat's gonna burst
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.56,0:11:09.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吃的热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:09.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yummy weenie
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我们正好赶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like we got here just in time
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴再见到你  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good to see ya, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.24,0:11:29.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能回来真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:29.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, it sure is great to have you back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sigh
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托拔了我电源吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please unplug me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.42,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFB5&}困在电梯里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:38.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(716,406)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:38.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(734,698)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:43.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(610,468)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(774,684)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:41.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(740,548)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(596,560)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(640,598)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.30,0:11:49.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灵感的肚皮就蕴藏在你的勇气中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:49.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The belly of inspiration lies in the midst of your gut"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.39,0:11:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好把这本好书还给图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welp, I better return
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this wonderful book to the library
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免得逾期了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before it's due
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站得太靠近的事我是怎么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what did I tell you about standing too close to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.12,0:12:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你一直要站得太靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you keep standing too close to me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就会被你绊倒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to trip over you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.21,0:12:17.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必多言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:17.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I rest my case
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更不必变脸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and my face
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想邀请你跟我和派大星一起出游
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to invite you to go with me and Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们今天的安排可好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have a really fun day planned
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的是好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shucks and golly gee
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真希望能来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really wish I could come
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你和派大星玩得特开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and have big fun with you and Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.73,0:12:34.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:34.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.19,0:12:39.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是我得把我最爱的每日金句书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:36.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I have to return
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my favorite book of daily affirmations
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶在中午之前还给图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the library by noon
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然就得受罚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or I'll have to pay a penalty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说这本书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean this book?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.62,0:12:50.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生活中  与树木捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:50.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"In life, 'tis better to play hide-and-seek with the trees
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,优于与微风下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than checkers with the wind"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星就会说这种金句
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what Patrick always says
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, he doesn't
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.42,0:12:57.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自个找金句去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:57.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get your own affirmations
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,366)}欢乐时光\N快艇
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we go
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(814,848)}图书馆
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早上九点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,9:00 a.m.--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离到期还早着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,plenty of time before the deadline
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  得早起才可以早来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you have to get up pretty early in the morning
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而我也早起了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I did
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.91,0:13:28.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:28.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There it is--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还书处  顶层
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,book returns, top floor
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.58,0:13:37.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要上楼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:37.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going up?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.17,0:13:39.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搭下趟得了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:39.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take the next one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.84,0:13:49.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:49.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.26,0:13:51.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挡门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:51.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold the door
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.85,0:13:52.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:52.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Close the door
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.43,0:13:52.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:52.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Close the door
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.93,0:13:53.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:53.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Close the door
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮忙挡门  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for holding the door, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.61,0:14:12.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们俩白痴今天不是有啥好玩安排吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:12.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you yo-yos had a big day of fun planned
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.16,0:14:14.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:14.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you there?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就在玩啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are there, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为今天是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because today is
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐电梯日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Elevator Riding Day
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.96,0:14:28.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我虽怒火中烧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:28.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel my anger
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.26,0:14:32.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但又如一盘意大利扁面一般冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:32.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I am calm like a plate of linguine
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, be a dear
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我按一下顶层的按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and hit the top-floor button for me, please
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顶层
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Top floor
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.06,0:14:40.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上楼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:40.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going up--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先把其他楼的按钮都按了再说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,right after we hit all these other floors
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少按了一颗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You missed one
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.53,0:14:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一层都不能落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every floor counts
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先上顶楼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Top floor first
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先上顶楼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Top floor first
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了  我们被困了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, we're trapped
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,困得跟沙丁鱼似的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,trapped like sardines
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.13,0:15:08.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们向来都出这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:08.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This happens to us all the time
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.13,0:15:11.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  上周咱就只等了五小时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:11.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, last week we only had to wait five hours
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五小时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Five hours"?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都已经超过还书期限了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's past the book-return deadline
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如一盘意大利扁面一般
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like a plate of linguine
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.06,0:15:26.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然就打一下紧急电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:26.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't we just use the emergency phone
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来求救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and call for help?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.61,0:15:31.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想从简就从简吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:31.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you want to do it the easy way
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.87,0:15:35.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:35.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.99,0:15:36.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:36.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没想到这电话居然还能用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't think this phone would work
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.17,0:15:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没想到这电话居然还能用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't think this phone would work
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被困在电梯里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trapped in an elevator
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被困在电梯里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trapped in an elevator
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.30,0:15:49.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别学我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:49.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop saying what I'm saying
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别学我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop saying what I'm saying
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.72,0:15:54.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真被困在电梯里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:54.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really am trapped in an elevator
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.01,0:15:57.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真被困在电梯里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:57.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really am trapped in an elevator
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.77,0:15:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:15:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一点忙都帮不上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're no help at all
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一点忙都帮不上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're no help at all
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.56,0:16:04.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:04.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.11,0:16:10.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放松是跃向宁静的脚尖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:10.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Relaxation is the tippy toe to tranquility"
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.65,0:16:14.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就放松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:14.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you relax
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星修得好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick can fix it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.20,0:16:21.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  我爸当过一整天的电梯医生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:21.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my dad was an elevator surgeon for a whole day
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他当过什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was a what?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,螺丝刀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Screwdriver
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.34,0:16:35.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来接上正确的线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:35.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now to connect the right wires
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是这根
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.10,0:16:40.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:40.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, don't
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.53,0:16:57.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:57.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get me out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这破门怎么就是不开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why won't these stupid doors open?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.92,0:17:14.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:14.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grab my hand
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好险啊  对吧章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a close one, huh, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A door
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.00,0:17:46.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:46.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你们好运  废物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck, losers
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.42,0:17:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.34,0:17:54.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那本书总算可以按时归还了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:54.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, that book is getting returned on time
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're back
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我们推一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now give us a boost
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.81,0:18:13.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平静心境浮于奶酪之海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:13.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Serenity floats on an ocean of cheese"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我饿坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm starving
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们被困多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long have we been stuck in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.41,0:18:24.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不在电梯那会儿  我们订了匹萨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:24.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While you were out, I ordered a pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我  你这白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that, you pea brain
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以打电话求救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can call for help
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:30.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1312,490)}披萨馋嘴\N有送必达
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,匹萨外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pizza delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.63,0:18:37.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:37.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.72,0:18:39.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:39.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're saved
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.80,0:18:41.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:41.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.02,0:18:49.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:49.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's eat
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat what?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.82,0:18:59.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下我要饿死了  书也要逾期了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:59.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm starving, and my book is going to be late
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.20,0:19:04.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,仅当失去了一切  方能看清鼻孔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:04.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Only when all is lost can you see inside your nostrils
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找寻自己的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and find yourself"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,经历了很久的宁静之后
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm free
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,历经22年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After 22 years
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.77,0:19:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算逃出那间该死的电梯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I finally got out of that cursed elevator
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,W-what?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.48,0:19:37.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又一间电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:37.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another elevator?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings, stranger
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临我们的宁静之岛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to our island of tranquility
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上楼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going up
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.45,0:19:52.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比我先前的电梯好上个不少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:52.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a lot nicer than my old elevator
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,介意我待一会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mind if I stay here a while?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.09,0:19:58.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得问问大王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:58.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll have to ask the king
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上楼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going up
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.80,0:20:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The king?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.05,0:20:06.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁呼唤我的大名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:06.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did someone say my name?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.51,0:20:08.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睿智的章鱼哥大王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:08.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, wise King Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.43,0:20:11.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位疲惫的旅人期望能与我们暂留
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:11.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This weary traveler wishes to stay with us
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.39,0:20:12.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托了  大王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:12.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, King
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能留下他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can we keep him?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我查查书
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me consult the book
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.32,0:20:25.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,书
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:25.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The book
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,书
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The book
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.87,0:20:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,患难见忠仆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"A friend in need is a servant guaranteed"
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,书同意你留下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The book says yes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上楼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going up
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.38,0:20:42.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你当然可以与我们暂留  我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:42.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course you can stay with us, my child
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.84,0:20:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会向你传授书中之道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll teach you the ways of the book
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.84,0:20:51.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就必须每天崇拜我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:51.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you'll get to spend every day worshipping me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.35,0:20:57.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会变得跟我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:57.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll be just like us
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.06,0:20:59.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:20:59.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, gee
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.36,0:21:01.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是门铃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:01.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that the doorbell?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.57,0:21:03.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  我好像忘关烤箱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:03.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I-I think I left the oven on
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  我的臣民
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, my people
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.87,0:21:12.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,书上说  现在是我的休息时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:12.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the book says it's time for me to relax
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.04,0:21:13.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:13.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面的都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you all right in there?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对对  我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I'm all right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.96,0:21:18.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:18.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get me out
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.80,0:21:23.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:23.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.59,0:21:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们救我逃离这些傻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for rescuing me from these stupid--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是章鱼哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you Squidward Tentacles?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.43,0:21:28.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:28.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.89,0:21:30.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一直都在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:30.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've been looking for you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是图书馆警察
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're the library police
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.85,0:21:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有一本借书已逾期30秒未还
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:34.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have a withdrawn book
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that is now 30 seconds overdue
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.90,0:21:39.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因此你必须受罚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:39.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you'll have to pay the penalty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do I owe you--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.32,0:21:41.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,像是罚款一毛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:41.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like, a nickel?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.23,0:21:45.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要进图书馆监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:45.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to library jail
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,图书馆监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Library jail--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.37,0:21:50.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是放松
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:50.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how relaxing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.95,0:21:55.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我花时间养精蓄锐  以此赏识自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:55.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"I appreciate myself by taking time to recharge
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.04,0:21:57.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还陪着我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:57.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"with my best friend--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.08,0:21:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.67,0:22:09.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睿智的大王啊  我们好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.67,0:22:09.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, wise king, we missed you so
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.89,0:22:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么  海神王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, Neptune?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.60,0:22:16.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们也有书逾期了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:16.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We had overdue books, too
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上楼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going up
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.11,0:22:24.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上楼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:25.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(968,752)}本集完
